Package org.gicentre.tests Description

Testing classes for use with the gicentreUtils library.

This package includes unit tests and example sketches to test the classes in the gicentreUtils library.

To check you have the latest version of the gicentreUtils package, display the results of Version.getText() or Version.getVersion(). It should match that shown in this API documentation.
